  <brief_title>Effect of Carbonated Soft Drinks on Appetite-Regulation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Carbonated Soft Drinks May Alter Appetite Sensation and Appetite-Regulating Hormone Level and Lead to Increased Energy Intake.</official_title>
